item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Missing LOONA Songs (FLAC 24-Bit)
item.description:
Hi!

So, I was filling out my collection of LOONA songs in the highest quality possible for archival purposes and I noticed that there are a collection of random songs that are available on Bugs Korea in 24-bit FLAC that I can not find on the internet for download. It would be greatly appreciated if someone could share them.

I will also be linking each song back to it's Bugs Korea page in case someone can download it from there and upload it

OT12
  • X X
    (This is the only song off of [X X] that I cannot find in 24-bit flac. The rest of the album I can, however I can only find this song in the 10 mb 16-bit flac form, when it's supposed to be twice that size. I've looked everywhere and I still cannot find it.)
  • Pose
    (The rest of [Flip That] is only available in 16-bit flac, however this song was released earlier for Queendom 2, in which it is available in 24-bit flac.)
COCOMONG
  • Yum-Yum
  • Yummy-Yummy
QUEENDOM 2
  • PTT (Paint The Town) (Queendom 2 Ver.)
  • Shake It
  • Don't Go (Queendom 2 Ver.)
  • Tell Me Now
  • Butterfly (Queendom 2 Ver.)
  • JINAON
OSTS
  • Jinsoul - As Time Goes
  • Chuu - Spring Flower
  • A-FLOW - YOU
  • Chuu - Hello
  • Chuu - Loving U
  • Chuu - World Is One 2021
  • Heejin & Jinsoul - Masquerade
  • Chuu & B.I. - Lullaby
  • Heejin - Honestly
  • Chuu - Brunch
OTHER
  • We Wanna Be Adults
    (OST that Chuu did for Princess Pring in 2015. There is no 24-bit available, but I have not been able to find a regular flac, so a 16-bit flac of this would be much appreciated.)
  • Loonatic (English Version)
    (I have not been able to find this on Bugs or Melon or on any other korean streaming service, so I don't think a 24-bit flac is available. However, if someone can find it, please share.)
